      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Why American Range Appliances Require Specialized Repair</h3>

      <p>
        American Range appliances are built around professional-style cooking performance, powerful burners,
        rangetop flexibility, wall oven precision, and specialty cooking options that should not be treated
